727256f-a.title: Queens: Little Neck Parkway - Pembroke Avenue
727256f-a.text:
Little neck Parkway, south from near Pembroke Avenue (below
Northern Boulevard). Note, on the right, the Community Church
of Little Neck..
Anril 12, 1927
P. L. Sperr
